title: Detective Comics 23.2 (2013) (Tablet Edition)
description:
I adjusted the resolution and compression of the original scan for easier reading on tablets and to save space. All credit goes to the original scanner for their hard work. I have added 'Tablet Edition' to the name to avoid confusion.

Enjoy and please seed back.



Detective Comics 23.2 (Harley Quinn)

By:   	Matt Kindt, Neil Googe, Chris Burnham	
Type:   	Comics
Genres:   	Superhero
Publisher:   	DC Comics	
Pub. Date:  	September 11, 2013
Format:         CBZ

If Dr. Harleen Quinzel wasn't crazy when she fell for The Joker at Arkham Asylum, she sure was messed up afterwards!

Find out more from Harley's time with her beloved Mr. J. and see what got her into so much trouble that she was "recruited" for the Suicide Squad!
